<title>USA: Ormet invests $25 million to upgrade aluminum mill.</title>
<headline>Ormet invests $25 million to upgrade aluminum mill.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ormet Corp said it has just invested more than $25 million to modernize its aluminum rolling mill in Hannibal, Ohio.</p>
<p>The capital investments included gauge and shape control improvements to the plant's hot mill and tandem cold rolling mill, and installation of a new ingot scalper.</p>
<p>Ormet is a producer of primary aluminum.</p>
<p>((New York Commodity Desk 212-859-1646))</p>
